values: Hello everyone, I've decided to make my journal Friends Only. I want to be sure of who will watch these entrys because there are some information about me and others that I don't want to be open for everyone who stumbles across. This journal of mine has my personal stuff and difficulties, dolls, drawings and whatever I can come up with. If you're still interested please leave me a comment here (And where I might know you from) so I can add you.
